anarcho-syndicalist


worked with AIT --> CNT-AIT

also worked with Federacion Anarquista Iberica (FAI) --> CNT-FAI

1910 - founded

"We make no distinction at the time of admission, we require only that you are a worker, student or unemployed. The only people who cannot join are those belonging to repressive organisations (police, military, security guards), employers or other exploiters"
